<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>قَنَتَ فِي الْوِتْرِ قَبْلَ الرُّكُوعِ» .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَأَبَانٌ مَتْرُوكٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢٠٩ - وَرَوَى أَنَسٌ عَنْهُ أَنَّهُ <span class="c2">«قَنَتَ بَعْدَ الرُّكُوعِ»</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَهُوَ الْأَصَحُّ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٢١٠ -<span class="c5"> وَقَدْ صَحَّ عَنْ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ قَنَتَ شَهْرًا يَدْعُو عَلَى قَوْمٍ مِنَ الْمُشْرِكِينَ»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>